{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/ENG1_png.png?t=1736852472\" /><br>Embark on an otherworldly adventure with Backrooms Media, a multiplayer co-op game that plunges you into surreal, hyper-realistic liminal spaces where the line between dream and reality blurs. Navigate eerie environments filled with lurking horrors and mysterious landscapes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/Entity-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1736852472\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/ENG2_png.png?t=1736852472\" /><br>You don't have to go alone. Team up with friends to face the terror of the endless backrooms together and try to find your way out. Your survival hinges on collaboration. Use proximity voice chat to share discoveries, strategize, and tackle the challenges. Whisper strategies in real-time, only audible to nearby teammates, and adapt on the fly as the immersive audio heightens the cooperative experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/backrooms_media-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1736852472\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/ENG3_png.png?t=1736852472\" /><br>High-quality graphics, powered by Unreal Engine 5, deliver an immersive experience that brings the unsettling environments to life with stunning realism. Coupled with your bodycam's nostalgic VHS visuals, every moment is captured in haunting detail, transporting you to a time and place beyond explanation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/Lab.gif?t=1736852472\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/ENG4_png.png?t=1736852472\" /><br>For user-generated content enthusiasts, Backrooms Media offers a powerful level editor, enabling you to create and share your own nightmarish environments. Challenge others to survive the horrors you\u2019ve designed in the backrooms.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2714970/extras/LevelEditor-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1736852472\" /><br><br><strong>Are you ready to face the unknown and uncover the secrets of the Backrooms? Gather your friends, gear up, and dive into Backrooms Media.</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Research Laboratory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/c54df274d4956b8daad95d3112342066ffd64562.jpg"},{"name":"Level0","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/ce6e981ae0751630dd8b0195bb382a7111d46355.jpg"},{"name":"Deep in Level0","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/84b11fad38c2891f683d07792f51f312ba2e45af.jpg"},{"name":"Parking Hub","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/369497b30206ee179f1756993e6abf8d69e91068.jpg"},{"name":"PipeDreams","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/71492214c7ddac34aea31277cf29791f77134c80.jpg"},{"name":"Sewer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/4815cbbb6bb876689627771084ea355c1118416d.jpg"},{"name":"Office","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/581155abe9d3d18c632b8be7b9a378f7c53caf0b.jpg"},{"name":"Poolrooms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2714970/5bcf7548335812b8977a781fe9c621463bab6251.jpg"},{"name":"Electrical Station","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/ima